
<div id="full-screen-picture">
  <div class="container d-flex flex-column" style="height:100%">
    <div class="container-searchbar d-flex flex-column align-items-center search-position-top" >
      <div class = "searchbar">
        <%= render 'shared/logomove' %>
        <%= render 'shared/searchbar' %>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center text-under-search">
        <h1 id="counter"><%= number_with_delimiter(@global_money, :delimiter => ',') %>€</h1>
        <div id="sentence">
          <p>raised to support equality
          thanks to your <span class="green-text"><%= number_with_delimiter(@global_search_count, :delimiter => ',') %> </span >searches.</p>
        </div>
        <h4>Thank you !</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="align-self-end legend-size">
      <h4 class="underline"> Simone Veil</h4>
      <p> French political figure, she served as Health Minister in several governments and was President of the European Parliament from 1979 to 1982, the first woman to hold that office. As health minister, she is best remembered for advancing women’s legal rights in France, in particular for the 1975 law that legalized abortion, today known as Loi Veil.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-bellow">
  <div class="card-presentation">
    <div id=image-one></div>
    <div class=container-text>
      <h4 class="title">Each time you search, EQUALS funds pro-feminists and pro-LGBT charities:</h4>
      <p class="text">EQUALS is like any other search engine, with one major difference: we use our profits to fund charities supporting feminists and LGBT causes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-presentation">
    <div class=container-text id="container-text-two">
    <h4 class="title">Choose the causes that resonate to you:</h4>
    <p class="text">You can pick the charities you want to support with your searches.</p>
    </div>
    <div id=image-two></div>
  </div>
  <div class="banner">
    <div class="text-banner">
    <p>Your searches make the world a better place.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-cards">
    <div class= cards-infos>
      <div id="card-one">
      </div>
      <div class="text-cards">
       <h6>We don't track you</h6>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us so we don't  sell your data to third parties and make sure to anonymize all your searches</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class= cards-infos>
      <div id="card-two">
      </div>
      <div class="text-cards">
       <h6>We take care of your causes</h6>
       <p>We follow the funds you gave to the charities and give you updates on how the charities acted for your causes</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class= cards-infos>
      <div id="card-three">
      </div>
      <div class="text-cards">
       <h6>We are CO2 neutral</h6>
       <p>Our server run on renewable energy and we compensate all the CO2 generated by EqualS</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



